      "Lead the migration from Vue 3 to Nuxt 3, improving application performance and SEO.",
      "Lead the development of a landing page using Nuxt 3, contributing to user acquisition.",
      "Actively contributed to the project's architecture and structure, ensuring it was well-organized, effective, and scalable.",
      "Contributed to UI Kit development, improving design consistency and frontend efficiency.",
      "Researched and incorporated Storybook for UI Kit, facilitating component testing and documentation.",
      "Contributed to performance optimizations and SEO.",
      "Configured and managed essential tools (Webpack, Vite, Eslint, Stylelint, Prettier, etc.).",
